mmerson_Bockarie\", \"score\": 0.9999987807153204, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmerson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmerson_Bockarie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmerson_Bockarie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a 3.30am inspection of the Seine, Paris chiefs decided to push back the event after deeming pollution levels to be too high.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.636261413894574e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.300438954140153e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, organisers said heavy rain over Paris over the weekend had forced them to 'reschedule the event for health reasons'.And Emmerson, speaking to BBC Radio 5 Live, has now revealed athletes are 'unhappy' and 'disappointed' with the decision.Olympics 2024: Team GB stars are 'unhappy' and 'disappointed' after the men's triathlon was delayed due to concerns over the Seine|GETTY\\\"It's looking very eerie.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.300438954140153e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmerson_Bockarie\", \"score\": 0.9999987807153204, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmerson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmerson_Bockarie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmerson_Bockarie\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBC Radio 5 Live\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There should have been an absolutely amazing atmosphere,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lots of people have come out because they do not realise the triathlon has been postponed.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The water does not look great and there is also a really strong current as well.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have said that the women's race will take place at eight o'clock in the morning [tomorrow] as was scheduled and then the men's at 10:45.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it is slightly up in the air, it's 50/50 still but that's what they said at 03:30 this morning.JUST IN:'Disqualify them' - Olympic officials told to boot Rafael Nadal and Carlos Alcaraz out of doubles draw\\\"Strange time to make the decision as there were athletes that had gone to bed thinking they were getting up to do a triathlon today which is obviously not happening.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of very unhappy athletes, very disappointed with the decision that has been made.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is the right decision, of course.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes cannot swim here.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of the location and the choice of the venue, that is what is in question now.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People have planned meticulously to start at 8am this morning and they are just going to have to make those changes and stay calm.READ MORE:England add another name to next manager shortlist as three 'favourites' emerge to replace Gareth Southgate\\\"Some athletes will fare a lot better than others.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some will go with it and others will be pretty stressed by it.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Vicky Holland, who won bronze in the women's triathlon at Rio in 2016, has also branded the controversy 'not great'.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2358, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicky Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7489244101642389, \"rank\": 0.3352482392452256, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's of course not ideal in any way, this sort of thing to happen.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without wishing to make it a bigger deal than it is, it's not great,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is something that has been spoken about endlessly, the water quality issues we have had here in Paris.LATEST SPORTS NEWS:Olympics fans convinced Clare Balding made X-rated blunder during BBC coverage - 'I am not mishearing am I?\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare Balding\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\"}, {\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.7994439428877383, \"rank\": 0.2508598989639144, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Novak Djokovic makes complaint after thumping Olympics win over Rafael NadalRafael Nadal snaps at question after emphatic Olympics defeat to Novak Djokovic - 'You ask me the same thing'Olympics: The men's triathlon has been delayed due to concerns over the Seine River|PA\\\"It's something we have known about for years, it's just not in the recent months.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do believe there had been a real attitude now, especially among the athletes and the British team that it will be alright on the day.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3295, \"end\": 3302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.915682968688823, \"rank\": 0.08961335116112272, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, there had been contingencies in place and we had planned that there might have to be a change, but I do not think anyone though it would happen, yet here we are.\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the moment, the water quality at the moment is not quite good enough.\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There had been a lot of rain around the opening ceremony and day one of competition.\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's unfortunately washed a lot of stuff off the streets to the Seine, that's now coming through the river and we are hoping that it will pass in time for the water quality testing that will happen before tomorrow morning.\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3735, \"end\": 3740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.636261413894574e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will know in 24 hours whether that has happened.Olympics: Vicky Holland has vented her fury after the men's triathlon was pushed back|PA\\\"All being well, hopefully we will get two races out tomorrow.\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 4095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3955, \"end\": 3968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicky Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From an athlete point of view, the men just have to keep their nerve.\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's only a 24 hour delay, not ideal, they have probably had a disrupted night's sleep.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now, it is as much mental as it is physical.\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Things could yet worsen, with thunder and lightning scheduled for Wednesday.Some family members of Team GB stars are concerned they may not be able to watch their loved ones in action, with fears that their tickets might not be valid for the re-arranged time of Wednesday.\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4404, \"end\": 4411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999558862040168, \"rank\": 3.208060435460371e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, organisers said heavy rain over Paris over the weekend had forced them to 'reschedule the event for health reasons'.\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4627, \"end\": 4632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.300438954140153e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.